<br>
While useful for most casting classes, it's exceptionally useful for clerics who are able to parasite all their HP for mana, and then complete heal themselves.  <br>
<br>
The item became so heavily imbalanced that characters were accepted or turned down for raids/groups on the basis of whether or not they possessed a manastone.  Eventually it was removed from the drop table, and restricted to use in old world zones (ie: Antonica, Faydwyr, Odus).<br>
<br>
